title: Henrik Uber alles
overview: Henrik Uber alles is a series about Henrik Thodesen and what happens when he becomes an Uber driver, whilst trying to kickstart his career as a comedian again. Henrik struggles to get assignments, and ends up increasingly in the shadow of his successful celebrity friends. In eight episodes we follow Henriks fight for the restarted career, and his relationship with Iben, a passenger he falls in love with.
